Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.60,0:24:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，基爾的秘密被揭開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.63,0:24:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.59,0:24:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
